---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout title="About Addy ‚Äì STEM Explorer" description="Learn more about Addy and her journey in STEM">
  <section class="container" style="padding:3rem 0 2rem;">
    <h1 class="section-heading">About Me</h1>
  </section>

  <section class="about-content container">
    <div class="about-card">
      <div class="about-intro">
        <h2>Hi, I'm Addy!</h2>
        <p class="lead">
          I'm a 5th grader who loves learning about math, science, and technology!
          This is my digital lab where I explore cool geometry concepts, discover amazing patterns,
          and learn about how computers work.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="interests-section">
        <h3>What I Love Learning About</h3>
        <div class="interests-grid">
          <div class="interest-card">
            <div class="interest-icon">üìê</div>
            <h4>Geometry</h4>
            <p>Learning about shapes, angles, and how they fit together. I think it's really cool how shapes can rotate and change size!</p>
          </div>
          <div class="interest-card">
            <div class="interest-icon">üßÆ</div>
            <h4>Math Formulas</h4>
            <p>Figuring out how to calculate volumes of 3D shapes. Math is like solving fun puzzles that actually work in real life!</p>
          </div>
          <div class="interest-card">
            <div class="interest-icon">ü§ñ</div>
            <h4>Raspberry Pi</h4>
            <p>Learning about these tiny computers that can do amazing things! I want to learn how to make them control lights and robots.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="interest-card">
            <div class="interest-icon">üé®</div>
            <h4>Patterns in Nature</h4>
            <p>Discovering how math creates beautiful patterns like Fibonacci spirals in sunflowers and seashells!</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="skills-section">
        <h3>What I'm Learning</h3>
        <div class="skills-categories">
          <div class="skill-category">
            <h4>Math & Science</h4>
            <ul>
              <li>Geometry & Angles</li>
              <li>Volume Calculations</li>
              <li>Pattern Recognition</li>
              <li>Problem Solving</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <div class="skill-category">
            <h4>Technology</h4>
            <ul>
              <li>Raspberry Pi Basics</li>
              <li>How Computers Work</li>
              <li>Electronics & Circuits</li>
              <li>Robotics Ideas</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <div class="skill-category">
            <h4>STEM Skills</h4>
            <ul>
              <li>Asking Good Questions</li>
              <li>Making Predictions</li>
              <li>Testing Ideas</li>
              <li>Creative Thinking</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="philosophy-section">
        <h3>Why I Love STEM</h3>
        <blockquote>
          "Math and science are everywhere! When you can see shapes moving and patterns forming,
          it's like magic but it's real. I love learning how things work and discovering
          that everything around us follows cool rules and patterns."
        </blockquote>
      </div>

      <div class="goals-section">
        <h3>What I Want to Learn Next</h3>
        <div class="goals-list">
          <div class="goal-item">
            <span class="goal-icon">ü§ñ</span>
            <div>
              <h4>Raspberry Pi Projects</h4>
              <p>I really want to get a Raspberry Pi and learn how to make it light up LEDs, maybe even control a robot someday!</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="goal-item">
            <span class="goal-icon">üìê</span>
            <div>
              <h4>More Geometry</h4>
              <p>Learning about more complex shapes and how to use geometry in the real world, like in buildings and bridges</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="goal-item">
            <span class="goal-icon">üî¨</span>
            <div>
              <h4>Science Experiments</h4>
              <p>Doing hands-on experiments to understand how physics works, like how things move and why objects fall</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <style>
    .section-heading {
      text-align: center;
      font-size: 2.5rem;
      margin-bottom: 2rem;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--color-primary), var(--color-secondary));
      -webkit-background-clip: text;
      -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
      background-clip: text;
    }

    .about-content {
      padding-bottom: 4rem;
    }

    .about-card {
      background: var(--color-surface);
      backdrop-filter: blur(20px);
      border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
      padding: 3rem;
      box-shadow: var(--shadow-soft);
      border: 1px solid var(--color-outline);
    }

    .about-intro {
      text-align: center;
      margin-bottom: 3rem;
      padding-bottom: 3rem;
      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-outline);
    }

    .about-intro h2 {
      font-size: 2.5rem;
      margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
      color: var(--color-ink);
    }

    .lead {
      font-size: 1.25rem;
      line-height: 1.8;
      color: var(--color-muted);
      max-width: 700px;
      margin: 0 auto;
    }

    .interests-section,
    .skills-section,
    .philosophy-section,
    .goals-section {
      margin-bottom: 3rem;
    }

    .interests-section h3,
    .skills-section h3,
    .philosophy-section h3,
    .goals-section h3 {
      font-size: 1.75rem;
      margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
      color: var(--color-ink);
      text-align: center;
    }

    .interests-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(240px, 1fr));
      gap: 1.5rem;
      margin-top: 2rem;
    }

    .interest-card {
      background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.5);
      padding: 1.5rem;
      border-radius: var(--radius-sm);
      text-align: center;
      transition: transform 0.3s ease;
    }

    .interest-card:hover {
      transform: translateY(-5px);
    }

    .interest-icon {
      font-size: 3rem;
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }

    .interest-card h4 {
      font-size: 1.25rem;
      margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
      color: var(--color-ink);
    }

    .interest-card p {
      color: var(--color-muted);
      line-height: 1.6;
      font-size: 0.95rem;
    }

    .skills-categories {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(200px, 1fr));
      gap: 2rem;
      margin-top: 2rem;
    }

    .skill-category {
      background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.5);
      padding: 1.5rem;
      border-radius: var(--radius-sm);
    }

    .skill-category h4 {
      font-size: 1.25rem;
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
      color: var(--color-primary);
    }

    .skill-category ul {
      list-style: none;
      padding: 0;
      margin: 0;
    }

    .skill-category li {
      padding: 0.5rem 0;
      color: var(--color-ink);
      position: relative;
      padding-left: 1.5rem;
    }

    .skill-category li:before {
      content: '‚ñπ';
      position: absolute;
      left: 0;
      color: var(--color-secondary);
    }

    blockquote {
      background: rgba(196, 182, 255, 0.15);
      border-left: 4px solid var(--color-primary);
      padding: 1.5rem 2rem;
      margin: 2rem 0;
      border-radius: var(--radius-sm);
      font-style: italic;
      color: var(--color-ink);
      line-height: 1.8;
      font-size: 1.1rem;
    }

    .goals-list {
      display: grid;
      gap: 1.5rem;
      margin-top: 2rem;
    }

    .goal-item {
      display: flex;
      gap: 1.5rem;
      background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.5);
      padding: 1.5rem;
      border-radius: var(--radius-sm);
      align-items: flex-start;
    }

    .goal-icon {
      font-size: 2rem;
      flex-shrink: 0;
    }

    .goal-item h4 {
      font-size: 1.2rem;
      margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
      color: var(--color-ink);
    }

    .goal-item p {
      color: var(--color-muted);
      line-height: 1.6;
    }

    @media (max-width: 768px) {
      .about-card {
        padding: 2rem 1.5rem;
      }

      .interests-grid {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      }

      .skills-categories {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      }

      blockquote {
        padding: 1rem 1.5rem;
      }

      .goal-item {
        flex-direction: column;
        gap: 1rem;
      }
    }
  </style>
</BaseLayout>
